# EGGuard — toolbox cron schedule
# ================================
# Install at:  /var/lib/enforcegate-toolbox/cron.d/egguard
# Edit via:    eghost toolbox cron edit
#
# The UT1 Capitole feed refreshes 2–3 times per week, so a daily run is plenty.
# Times are UTC unless ENFORCEGATE_TOOLBOX_TZ is set in the bundle's .env.
#
# Format: min hour dom mon dow  command
#
15 3 * * * python3 /var/lib/enforcegate-toolbox/repos/egguard/scripts/egguard update
